{"title": "How to Send SMS on Demand on the Patient Dashboard?", "body": "Follow these steps to Send SMS on Demand from the Patient Dashboard:\nOpen the Patient Record\nClick Dashboard to open the patient dashboard\nNavigate to the Quick Action toolbar\nClick the SMS on Demand Icon to open the SMS on Deman Fields.\nFill out the necessary field to start sending SMS. You may choose a template if you wish to use one, or you can also free type on the enter message field and click Send.\n "}